{"type":"message","id":"0b023e5f","parentId":"d8e9db5d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:23:08.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing image content**\n\nI need to derive an answer from the image understanding capabilities. If the user asks, \"这个啥问题\" (translation: \"What's the problem here?\"), I'll need to infer the issue based on the screenshot they provided. I might not be able to read everything clearly, so I could suggest asking for a clearer or more cropped version. Assuming the screenshot contains an error message, I should craft a likely diagnosis based on what I can interpret from the image dimensions and context.\n\n**Considering OCR options**\n\nI’m thinking about using OCR, but I can’t rely on local options like Tesseract. Instead, I might use the inherent vision capability to interpret the image data. If the user asks about the problem, I should formulate a response like, \"根据图看是 SSH/OpenSSL？可能有危险.\" If it's unclear due to blurriness, I can suggest they send me a clearer screenshot or highlight the specific error. I want my response to be honest and concise in Chinese, while avoiding any assumptions.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这张图里字有点小，我不想瞎猜。现在我只能大概看出**是报错页/异常提示**，但具体报错文案我这边看不清，没法负责任地下结论。  \n\n你直接发我下面任意一种，我就能马上帮你定位：\n1. **报错文字原文**复制出来  \n2. **只截报错那一小块**，放大一点  \n3. 顺手告诉我你当时在干嘛：**点了什么、在哪个页面、想做什么**  \n\n你要是懒得打字，就再发一张**只裁报错框**的图，我来给你拆。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":390,"output":876,"cacheRead":38400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39666,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773807772714}}
{"type":"message","id":"5821ab16","parentId":"0b023e5f","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:23:09.747Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5496c4f6b4a8b4bf7c48f63fc2b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 12:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5496c4f6b4a8b4bf7c48f63fc2b]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\n\nGateway service disabled.\n\nStart with: openclaw gateway install\n\nStart with: openclaw gateway\n\nStart with: systemctl --user start opencla\n\nw-gateway.service\n\nStart with: systemd user services are unav\n\nailable; install/enable systemd or run the\n\ngateway under your supervisor.\n\nStart with: If you're in a container, run\n\nthe gateway in the foreground instead of\n\nopenclaw gateway\n\nroot@openclaw:~/.openclaw#"}],"timestamp":1773807789743}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8e21a4d","parentId":"5821ab16","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:23:20.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 问题很直接：**不是 `feishu_oauth_batch_auth` 工具有问题，而是 Gateway 根本没跑起来**，所以相关能力注册完也用不了。\n\n你这段输出的关键信息是：\n\n- `Gateway service disabled.`\n- `Start with: openclaw gateway install`\n- 如果 systemd 用户服务不可用，就别走 service，**直接前台启动**：`openclaw gateway`\n\n简单说就是分两种情况：\n\n1. **正常 Linux / 有 systemd 用户服务**\n   - 先执行：`openclaw gateway install`\n   - 再执行：`systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service`\n\n2. **容器里 / 没有 systemd**\n   - 直接执行：`openclaw gateway`\n   - 让它前台跑着，不要指望 `systemctl --user`\n\n另外你截图里那行 `opencla / w-gateway.service` 是换行断了，实际命令应该是：\n`systemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service`\n\n如果你愿意，我可以下一步直接帮你判断：**你现在这是容器环境，还是正常主机环境**，然后告诉你该走哪条。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1894,"output":334,"cacheRead":37376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773807789745}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d8fe68c","parentId":"d8e21a4d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:23:45.309Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5496c3c944a8b2ef256e03de259\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 12:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5496c3c944a8b2ef256e03de259]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: 帮我判断"}],"timestamp":1773807825307}}
{"type":"message","id":"cb1aafb1","parentId":"7d8fe68c","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:24:02.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这不是代码报错，本质上是 **OpenClaw 的 gateway 没启动/当前环境没法按 systemd 用户服务方式启动**。\n\n你贴出来这几行已经把原因说得很直白了：\n\n- `Gateway service disabled.`  \n  → gateway 服务现在没在跑\n- `systemd user services are unavailable`  \n  → 当前环境大概率**没有可用的 systemd --user**，常见于容器、精简环境、某些 SSH/session 场景\n- `If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of openclaw gateway`  \n  → 如果你这台就是容器环境，**不要指望 systemctl --user**，直接前台启动更合适\n\n我给你直接下判断：\n\n### 这是啥问题\n**运行环境和 OpenClaw gateway 的启动方式不匹配。**  \n不是权限小毛病，是**服务管理方式不对**。\n\n### 优先怎么处理\n按你这个提示，先分两种情况：\n\n#### 情况 1：你就在容器里\n直接前台跑：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n别走 `systemctl --user ...` 那套。\n\n#### 情况 2：你是正常 Linux 主机，想装成服务\n先装：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway install\n```\n然后再启动：\n```bash\nsystemctl --user start openclaw-gateway.service\n```\n\n不过你这条提示里已经说了 **systemd user services are unavailable**，所以我更倾向于你现在是：\n- 容器里\n- 或者当前登录环境不支持 `systemd --user`\n\n### 我更偏向的结论\n**大概率是容器/无 systemd 用户服务环境，应该直接运行 `openclaw gateway`，不要用 systemctl。**\n\n### 你下一步可以这样确认\n发我这两个命令的输出，我就能给你定死：\n```bash\nopenclaw status\nps -p 1 -o comm=\n```\n\n如果第二条出来不是 `systemd`，那基本就坐实了。  \n你要的话，我也可以直接按你这个环境帮你给出**最短启动方案**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1302,"output":552,"cacheRead":38400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40254,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773807825308}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f8c42f5","parentId":"cb1aafb1","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:24:04.532Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5496c37a7cb4b2ceb69753c1624\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 12:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5496c37a7cb4b2ceb69753c1624]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: 我当前是lxc 容器"}],"timestamp":1773807844530}}
{"type":"message","id":"cfe4dc95","parentId":"4f8c42f5","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:24:18.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering LXC containers**\n\nI need to answer about LXC containers without using any tools. The user mentioned needing help with judging them, and I think it’s important to note that typically there are no systemd user services in LXC. Often, LXC doesn’t include a systemd user session. I’ll make sure my answer is concise while highlighting these points to help the user understand the limitations they might face with LXC containers!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 那基本就可以判了：**你这边按“容器环境”处理**，优先走 **前台启动 gateway**，别指望 `systemctl --user` 那套。\n\n直接用这条：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n原因很简单，LXC 里常见这两种情况：\n- **没有完整的 systemd 用户服务环境**\n- 就算有 systemd，也**不稳定或没开 user session**\n\n所以你刚才看到那句：\n> If you're in a container, run the gateway in the foreground instead of openclaw gateway\n\n意思就是：**在容器里不要折腾 user service，直接跑前台。**\n\n你现在建议这么做：\n\n1. 先执行\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway\n   ```\n2. 看它是不是正常启动、开始监听\n3. **保持这个进程运行着**\n4. 然后再回去试你刚才那个 Feishu 授权相关功能\n\n如果你想让它“后台常驻”，在 LXC 里通常要靠你自己的 supervisor，比如：\n- `screen`\n- `tmux`\n- `supervisord`\n- 容器自己的启动脚本\n\n**不建议你现在先搞 `openclaw gateway install`**，因为那条更偏向有完整 systemd/service 管理的环境。\n\n你要的话，我下一条可以直接给你一版 **LXC 容器里最稳的启动方式**，分成：\n- 临时跑起来\n- 后台常驻\n- 开机自启  \n三种给你。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1848,"output":463,"cacheRead":38400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773807844531}}
