{"type":"message","id":"14fd3544","parentId":"4a3b269d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:57:47.968Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，这说明**技能本体已经装好了，但还没完成 OKX 凭证配置**，所以现在只能跑到“检查依赖”这一步，不能真正调用后端。  \n\n你现在缺的是这 3 个：\n- `OKX_API_KEY`\n- `OKX_SECRET_KEY`\n- `OKX_PASSPHRASE`\n\n最稳的做法是：\n\n```bash\ncd /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace\ncat > .env <<'EOF'\nOKX_API_KEY=\"你的-api-key\"\nOKX_SECRET_KEY=\"你的-secret-key\"\nOKX_PASSPHRASE=\"你的-passphrase\"\nEOF\nchmod 600 .env\n```\n\n然后记得把 `.env` 加进 `.gitignore`，别进仓库：\n```bash\ngrep -qxF '.env' .gitignore || echo '.env' >> .gitignore\n```\n\n不过先提醒一句：**别把这三项直接发给我，也别贴在聊天里。**  \n你如果愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你做两件事之一：\n\n1. 给你一版**安全接入 OpenClaw / onchainos 的环境变量方式**  \n2. 带你去 **OKX Developer Portal** 看这三个值分别从哪拿"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":15175,"output":498,"cacheRead":33280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773853055308}}
