{"type":"message","id":"eeee16c5","parentId":"18dfb330","timestamp":"2026-03-18T16:58:10.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing deployment scenarios**\n\nI don't think we need to overthink it too much here. We could mention two scenarios: using the CLI for direct tests versus the persistent use of OpenClaw. \n\nIf the user is just testing on the onchainos CLI manually, I suggest placing the current project's `.env` in the project directory. For the OpenClaw workspace, the safest spot would be in `/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env`. \n\nTo ensure skills are recognized after a restart, it’s better to export them in the environment that starts the gateway, not just leave it in a random `.env`. Mentioning permissions like `chmod 600` and using gitignore could be useful too!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 放哪儿，取决于你是**自己手动跑 `onchainos`**，还是要让 **OpenClaw / gateway 也能用到**。这俩不是一回事。\n\n### 最实用的放法\n\n#### 方案 A：你只是先手动测试 CLI\n放到你当前工作目录的 `.env` 里就行。  \n按你现在这套环境，我建议先放这里：\n\n```bash\n/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n```\n\n内容类似：\n\n```env\nOKX_API_KEY=\"your-api-key\"\nOKX_SECRET_KEY=\"your-secret-key\"\nOKX_PASSPHRASE=\"your-passphrase\"\n```\n\n然后注意两件事：\n\n```bash\nchmod 600 /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n```\n\n以及确保 `.gitignore` 里有：\n\n```gitignore\n.env\n```\n\n---\n\n#### 方案 B：你想让 OpenClaw 里的技能长期可用\n那就**不能只靠一个随手放的 `.env` 文件**，关键是：\n\n> **启动 OpenClaw / gateway 的那个进程，得能拿到这 3 个环境变量。**\n\n也就是说，如果你现在是在 LXC 里前台跑：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n那最稳的是在**启动前先 export**：\n\n```bash\nexport OKX_API_KEY=\"your-api-key\"\nexport OKX_SECRET_KEY=\"your-secret-key\"\nexport OKX_PASSPHRASE=\"your-passphrase\"\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n这样当前这个 gateway 进程才能真正读到。\n\n---\n\n### 我给你的建议\n你现在先走这个最稳：\n\n1. 把凭证写到：\n   ```bash\n   /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n   ```\n2. 权限收紧：\n   ```bash\n   chmod 600 /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n   ```\n3. 启动前加载它：\n   ```bash\n   set -a\n   source /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace/.env\n   set +a\n   openclaw gateway\n   ```\n\n这样最省事。\n\n---\n\n### 别这么干\n- 不要把 key 直接发给我\n- 不要写进 `MEMORY.md`、`USER.md`、聊天记录、截图\n- 不要提交到 git\n- 不要放在 world-readable 权限的文件里\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以直接给你一份**可复制粘贴的完整命令**，帮你在 LXC 里把 `.env` 建好、权限收好、然后加载启动。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":494,"output":1306,"cacheRead":48256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50056,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773853069008}}
